data.name: HCS Orlando Major 2022
data.description: The final Major before the Halo World Championship! Team Passes will be on sale August 15th at 10:00 AM PT. Follow @HCS for updates!

tournaments.name: HCS Orlando Major 2022 FFA
tournaments.description: HCS Orlando Major 2022 features a free Halo FFA tournament, which will be open for up to 504 players and spectators. Best of luck to those competing!
